Please make sure to contact me to discuss your requirements before placing any orders.

So a little bit about what I can do for you; I create hand drawn black and white pen and ink illustrations, usually for album covers, but can be for other types of project as well. Themes I often work within include medieval/occult/folkhorror, but all is considered.

I like to keep things quite simple, whereby you tell me your ideas and I create a rough sketch for you so you can see if you like the general direction and want to make any adjustments. Then once you are happy, I'll work on the illustration and give you updates along the way so you can see how it is progressing. When complete I will share the drawing with you in JPEG or PNG format in high resolution.

Please also have a look through the gallery so you can be sure the style is right for your project. Drawings will be created in black and white or sepia pen and ink unless you request otherwise (other styles will need to be taken into consideration). Drawings are handmade which requires extra time and I believe the prices currently reflect this. I never use AI or copy and paste from other artworks.

Thanks! James

Title: I will create your fantasy map
Description:

I like to keep things quite simple, whereby you tell me your ideas and I create a rough sketch for you so you can see if you like the general direction and want to make any adjustments. Then once you are happy, I'll work on the illustration and give you updates along the way so you can see how it is progressing. When complete I will share the drawing with you in JPEG or PNG format in high resolution.

Please also have a look through the gallery so you can be sure the style is right for your project. Drawings will be created in black and white or sepia pen and ink unless you request otherwise (other styles will need to be taken into consideration). Drawings are handmade which requires extra time and I believe the prices currently reflect this. I never use AI or copy and paste from other artworks.

Thanks! James
